    "inputs" : {
    
    
    "para" :
    true,
    
    "html" :
    
    
    "To prevent programming from being aborted during software updates and any possible inconsistency in the hardware/software system due to user faults, the specifications for the battery chargers to be used and their necessary settings as well as the storage media (USB sticks) to be used must always be observed. Furthermore, no external devices (e.g. PIWIS Tester, smartphone, etc.) must be loaded in the vehicle via USB connections during control unit programming. "
    
    }
    
    }
